rns.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-08-12T08:46:33.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"owainlewis/awesome-artificial-intelligence","categoryHTML":"<h2>Learning</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/benedekrozemberczki/awesome-graph-classification\">Awesome Graph Classification</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/benedekrozemberczki/awesome-graph-classification\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.5k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":4478,\"repo\":\"benedekrozemberczki/awesome-graph-classification\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Learning from graph structured data</li>","updatedAt":"2022-08-12T08:46:33.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"owainlewis/awesome-artificial-intelligence","categoryHTML":"<h2>Journals</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"http://www.springer.com/journal/10472\">Annals of Mathematics and Artificial Intelligence</a></li>","updatedAt":"2022-08-12T08:46:33.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"erwanlemerrer/awesome-audit-algorithms","categoryHTML":"<h2>Papers</h2><h3>2018</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1710.06169\">Distill-and-Compare: Auditing Black-Box Models Using Transparent Model Distillation</a> - (AIES) <em>Treats black box models as teachers, training transparent student models to mimic the risk scores assigned by black-box models.</em></li>","updatedAt":"2022-08-12T08:01:02.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"denolib/awesome-deno","categoryHTML":"<h2>Modules</h2><h3>Utils</h3>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/roj1512/pls\">P